column5: Tell me,whats wrong           His name is       TERRY  Well done buddy.   The game is tied at 2..
wore the lucky lund hat, works every time
Nice couple a fatties there. Perfect pictures.
Bri, Bri...thought for sure by now it was common knowledge that if your name is Terry (Terrence for long)---you typically outfish anyone else in da boat  Heck I think that fact is even in Webster's
I'm guessing Terry caught his fish one at a time... the way it was intended.
Real walleye chop out there eh.
I'm guessing Terry caught his fish one at a time... the way it was intended.  Your close   Try again Rob.
yeah one at a time Im not the greedy one lol
Nice lakers bud! Never caught one, not for lack of trying...
LOL, a good friend keeps the sheep head out of the way so you can concentrate on the game fish?  Nice job!
What's wrong is that it wasn't you in the pictures and Terry taking them...!

What's wrong is that I don't see a few things in the pic... -nothing seems broken anywhere -Terry is smiling, sort of -I see no discarded smelt carcasses in the boat -Terry's beard is not stuffed full of bugs...  There, that's a start! HH
Terry has to perfect the grip and grin, he steelheads, he should know by now!    Nice job boys.
